dBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T12:57:13.000Z","msg":"香港傳媒被控制晒要減少香港人國際視野"},{"pid":"8b097d79288dcddca1a2417c8ffe92bf045c9976","tid":901583,"uid":81113,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T13:12:12.000Z","msg":"又話人地係恐怖分子<br />\n<br />\n又話「我們不會放棄與哈瑪斯的長期和平談判」<br />\n<br />\n點信<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8839df10d7c0f4084efd7012e3361ed298425765","tid":901583,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e22e6d5f71b15290d01ef69b36a570a0b3d8b516","tid":901583,"uid":63154,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1d0417e75685c623a196ed7cb2a7d1809d5dc02b","tid":901583,"uid":11148,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T06:48:12.000Z","msg":"咁大件事香港冇報導 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T12:57:13.000Z","msg":"香港傳媒被控制晒要減少香港人國際視野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T14:50:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 回教徒殺人放火一定狂報"},{"pid":"edf06341a5f22ca443c7cec95e576c14f6676acf","tid":901583,"uid":155732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7430ce9fbca56b030557233fa73811eef556d9e","tid":901583,"uid":82929,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T07:19:12.000Z","msg":"聯合國與歐盟方面皆呼籲「雙方自制」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聯合國執左佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T14:52:54.000Z","msg":"維和垃圾部隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n維條撚咩 日日叫雞飲酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd93f8785cd80193dd4e330458f19e5511a2a0f2","tid":901583,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0739e73dc3214120dcf4672fadefcd7c73727cd","tid":901583,"uid":34410,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f706939cb3727191dc034bc052cb98ed75ee89af","tid":9